This application uses gnupg.
You may need to install it first.
On Ubuntu issue "apt-get install gnupg".

Integration tests make use of php5-curl.
You may need to install it first.
On Ubuntu issue "apt-get install php5-curl".

When running Apache make sure the rewrite module is loaded.
If need be on Ubuntu issue "a2enmod /etc/apache2/mods-available/rewrite.load".

Configure your webserver to have htdocs/ as DocumentRoot.

There is an example apache vhost config file in docs/
TODO: There is an example nginx config file in docs/

To run this application you will need to configure it and take care of
access rights to the keyring to use.
@see README file